    dc:title "Review of the genus Argyresthia Hübner, [1825] (Lepidoptera: Yponomeutoidea: Argyresthiidae) from China, with descriptions of forty-three new species" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.827748>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.827750>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.827770>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.827752> ;
