<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.827748>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Wing venation of Argyresthia spp. 1, A. (Blastotere) aureola, sp. nov., slide no. LTT 12525 W, paratype; 2, A. (B.) cineretra, sp. nov., slide no. LTT 12402 W, paratype; 3, A. (Argyresthia) cardiopetala, sp. nov., slide no. LTT 12041 W, paratype; 4, A. (A.) punctuata, sp. nov., slide no. LTT 12536 W, paratype; 5, A. (A.) subrimosa Meyrick, slide no. LTT 1303 W; 6, A. (A.) lanosa, sp. nov., slide no. LTT 12635 W, paratype; 7, A. (A.) beta Friese & Moriuti, slide no. LTT 12481 W; 8, A. (A.) ellipsoidea, sp. nov., slide no. LTT 12385 W, paratype. (Scales = 2.0 mm)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/827748/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.827750>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 10. Genital structures of Argyresthia spp. 9, male genitalia, a – b, A. (Argyresthia) aphoristis Meyrick, 1938, slide no. LTT 12348, c – d, A. (Blastotere) anthocephala Meyrick, 1936, slide no. LTT 12312; 10, female genitalia, A. (A.) brockeella Hübner, [1805], slide no. LTT 12549. (Scales, 9 a – c = 0.2 mm, 9 d = 0.1 mm; 10 = 0.5 mm)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/827750/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.827770>
    dc:description "FIGURES 76 – 83. Live adults of Argyresthia spp. 76, A. (Blastotere) aureola, sp. nov.; 77, A. (B.) sporadolepis, sp. nov.; 78, A. (Argyresthia) mala, sp. nov.; 79, A. (A.) grammosacca, sp. nov.; 80, A. (A.) punctuata, sp. nov.; 81, A. (A.) brockeella (Hübner); 82, A. (A.) longalbella, sp. nov.; 83, A. (A.) kaoyaiensis Moriuti, by courtesy of Dr. Zhibo Wang (NKU)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/827770/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.827752>
    dc:description "FIGURE 11. Global distribution and biodiversity of Argyresthia derived from type localities." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/827752/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

